metadata.name: Beyond FOOD #1
metadata.description: In 2055, Beyond Food is the most beloved fast food brand in the Earth where autonomous vehicles operate perfectly. Beyond Food is one-bite-sized fast food that is printed in real time with 3D printer built into the vehicle. If you choose the ingredients and taste you want, you will find fun and beautiful food printed in one-bite-sized pieces that are easy to eat even in a moving car. In addition, this smart Beyond FOOD 3D food printer uses data such as age, health, interests to recommend optimized types. Beyond FOOD is the first NFT art work of the FUTURE PROJECT created by SUPERSQUARE. If you want to learn more about the project, visit the website. http://www.thesupersquare.io
